      <title>捷克通胀反弹，支撑谨慎宽松立场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/czech-inflation-rebounds-bolstering-cautious-stance-on-rates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[捷克通胀在第一季度达到央行目标后，上个月的增速超出预期，支持了采取更加谨慎的货币宽松政策的论点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/czech-inflation-rebounds-bolstering-cautious-stance-on-rates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 07:31:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>非洲顶级运营商 Vodacom 考虑合作以促进宽带发展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/largest-africa-carrier-vodacom-full-year-payout-misses-estimates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[非洲最大的无线运营商沃达康集团有限公司表示，它正在计划与其他移动运营商和金融投资者建立光纤合作伙伴关系，这可能会降低部署和农村连接的成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/largest-africa-carrier-vodacom-full-year-payout-misses-estimates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 05:16:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>碧桂园付出代价后，中国暂时避免了道德风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/china-averts-moral-hazard-for-now-after-country-garden-pays</link>
      <description><![CDATA[碧桂园控股公司支付债券利息后，中国一项旨在支持陷入困境的开发商债务的计划避免了其首次潜在干预，避免了此类支持可能引发的道德风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/china-averts-moral-hazard-for-now-after-country-garden-pays</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 01:52:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
